{"tid":1399310,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<軍政府> 警方：號召集體罷工是不負責任的言論","createTime":"2019-08-03T06:19:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T13:49:10.000Z","uid":227801,"like":4,"dislike":76,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"760993fa4769f9ae504d95281f5b435ccb7aeca9","tid":1399310,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T06:19:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=357791\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D357791&d=MMgAXMBwwZFGDPTkcL6JsaC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=fc34cf52\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D357791&h=de6f530d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=357791</a><br />\n【Now新聞台】警方指留意到網上有人號召下周一集體罷工，形容這是不負責任的言論，警方表示遺憾，而堵塞交通的行為亦是違法並影響緊急服務，警方會追究到底。<br />\n<br />\n警方又指，會與各總區的交通部及運輸署密切溝通和監察情況，準備應變計劃，至於當日七個地區都有集會，警方指目前只收到其中五區申請不反對通知書，會與主辦者溝通並進行風險評估，再決定是否批出不反對通知書。"},{"pid":"d39509c01352f6d379f0dcacedad24571ec8ad03","tid":1399310,"uid":11436,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T06:21:29.000Z","msg":"罷工又關你地班毅進狗事<br />\n軍政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22f79172177aa311d836a396f81fe015a28f8791","tid":1399310,"uid":120715,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T06:21:58.000Z","msg":"之前有ching好似post過基本法入面<br />\n寫住有罷工集會嘅自由"},{"pid":"8302e8e7e976e90c5c40152b87b7b6aa43f8f91d","tid":1399310,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T06:22:03.000Z","msg":"關你撚事？"},{"pid":"0188b2d9a170d1d51594f774fab1b1f3bb795c35","tid":1399310,"uid":41861,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T06:22:04.000Z","msg":"政府發言人轉左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87513eac03427bc719eeafd30526350c2141d